videos.description: Jarrett Culver gets the dish from David Moretti and knocks down the 3-pointer for the Red Raiders in the first half.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Culver drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Norense Odiase gets the feed from Niem Stevenson and finishes strong in the first half.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Odiase throws down two-handed jam

videos.description: Udoka Azubuike gets the lob from Devonte' Graham and finishes with the flush for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Kansas' Azubuike climbs ladder for alley-oop

videos.description: Devonte' Graham squares up his defender and sinks a deep 3-pointer for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham splashes home 3

videos.description: Devonte' Graham finds a trailing Udoka Azubuike who bangs through bodies on his way to the rim.
videos.headline: Kansas' Azubuike posterizes defender

videos.description: Zhaire Smith penetrates the Jayhawk defense and sinks the mid-rage jumper for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith knocks down step-back jumper

videos.description: Devonte' Graham puts on the jets and heads to the rack finishing through the contact.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham attacks the rim for and-1 layup

videos.description: Zhaire Smith gets the inbounds pass from Keenan Evans and slams it home for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith throws down inbounds pass

videos.description: Fran Fraschilla and Jon Scaimbi welcome Kennan Evans to the broadcast as the Red Raiders upset the Jayhawks 85-73.
videos.headline: Texas Tech records first ever win at Allen Fieldhouse
